  "translations": {
    "en": "who said: A man spoke disparagingly of 'Ali ibn Abi Talib in the presence of 'Umar ibn al-Khattab, so 'Umar said to him: Do you know who owns this grave? Muhammad ibn 'Abdillah ibn 'Abd al-Muttalib and 'Ali ibn Abi Talib ibn 'Abd al-Muttalib. Do not mention 'Ali except in goodness, for if you disparage him you will hurt this one in his grave.",
